@NODE future "StopMenu Documnentation - Future"


@{b}9. Future@{ub}


There are many things which I could still improve in my program. My first plan
is to remove as many remaining bugs as possible. After that I could start
adding new functions to the program. I already have many of own ideas and also
suggestions from other users.

In spite of all that I said till now I am not quite sure how much longer and
further I am still going to develop this program because of the announced
future of Amiga. Though, I'll still very probably at least get rid of most of
the bugs if my Amiga lets me do it (occasionally it is really having some
hard times).

Last but not least. Incoming registrations always encourage me to do some
further development. @{"Register" LINK register} and you'll do something to prolong the
development of this program.


@ENDNODE
